title: Tables
---
p.-text Tables are used to present data sets in a simple and organized way.

h3 Requirements
p.-text
  | Tables must be wrapped in a <code>&lt;section class="a-table"&gt;</code>
  | with a nested <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>. The table must have the
  | <code>cellpadding</code> and the <code>cellspacing</code> set to <code>0</code>
  | and table header text must be wrapped with a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>.
